				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Doesnt Puretone only affect Singing based songs? </span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
No it affects both your singing and instrument modifiers.  Once you get IM3/SM3, the benefit from puretone (assuming you have your epic) starts to be rather minor.
<br />

<br />
I rarely use puretone anymore, but I did use it before I had TDoK and IM3/SM3.  I occasionally use it on big bad boss mobs for a bit extra atk from zek or resists from psalm.</span></td>
